Hello Dubai!

I recently had the opportunity to travel Dubai, a destination that’s been on my bucket list for quite some time.

The first morning I woke up I had the beach all to myself. I stayed right near the Iconic Burj Al Arab Jumeirah… such an incredible building!

#Dubai #BohnVoyage

Such a “pinch me” moment!

It was such an honour to work with @gaggenauofficial appliances and @avantgarde_dubai.

The opportunity to share my business and personal branding story to a room full of architects and designers from the Middle East was a dream come true. I hope you all learned a thing or two about personal branding as well. 😉

Here are a few photos from the #limitlessimagination event.

Dubai photo dump.

It’s always been on my bucket list to visit Dubai. It was a total dream come true to team up with @avantgarde_dubai for the @gaggenauofficial event. Beyond the architecture and design, the people I met made this trip incredible!

WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN?!

“We miss you on YouTube!” 

You guys have been so great at reminding me how much my content impacts you. And I love you for that. 

Truthfully, I took a giant step back and a big break from making content in 2023. I never intended to take a break, I just felt this strange resistance every time I would turn the camera on or try to edit something. Uploading a post just felt like this monumental task. 

Sure, I’ve been making a few posts from my design work here and there, but I certainly haven’t been showing up the way that you’re use to seeing me… or the way I wanted to show up. Something just didn’t FEEL right. 

I really needed to take a break from social media and 2023 became the year that I ‘accidentally’ did a year-long digital detox.

I can’t tell you how nourishing, soul-rejuvenating and inspiring it’s been to put down my phone and focus on REAL LIFE - my baby, my husband, my friends, my team, my personal development and spiritual growth. 

Gosh, there’s so much that I want to share with you now that I’m re-energized and feel like my cup is full again. But since IG caption space is probably going to run out here… let’s just say I am SO excited to see and share more with you in 2024. 

Let’s gooooooooo!! 

Love you. xxK
